overview:
CARGO CATS, INC. provides warehousing, order fulfillment, trucking, shipping, logistics and distribution services. They offer railcar unloading, cross docking, distribution and warehousing services in California.

About Company:

CARGO CATS, INC. is a third party logistics provider which operates as an asset based corporation along with providing non-asset based services to assure best practice partners in achieving their goals of a cost efficient, flexible and integrated supply chain. They offer railcar unloading, cross docking, distribution and warehousing services in California.
